{"tid":2498444,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車迷憤怒聚集示威！施治被罵成「叛徒」","createTime":"2021-04-21T07:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T08:11:51.000Z","uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b690167ff018e99652c839ac6b65ae2ba47a466f","tid":2498444,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"車路士與白禮頓賽前，球迷聚集在史坦福橋場外，攔阻藍軍球隊大巴，施治（Petr Cech）不得不下來做工作。<br />\n<br />\n  憤怒的藍軍球迷攔住道路，抗議車路士此前加入歐超聯賽的舉動，甚至不讓準備進入球場的大巴車通過。藍軍名宿、車路士技術總監施治不得不來到人群中，懇請球迷讓路。警察在施治身邊組成了保護網，而有一些憤怒的球迷，甚至呼喊施治為「叛徒」。<br />\n<br />\n  今天淩晨，英超六強已經全部退出了歐超聯賽，這場造反行動以失敗告終。<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2021/04/21/a/a7dc097bd3db090ae71053f7fe539fbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2021%2F04%2F21%2Fa%2Fa7dc097bd3db090ae71053f7fe539fbc.jpg&h=695945a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b2bc2adc33c566de643d714acf7d9353d8328f2","tid":2498444,"uid":243550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:23:50.000Z","msg":"法國啲鬼佬好鍾意講嘢嘅時候蚊抵個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3257b84a11a5aa8baf93bf72621ba353d3152d","tid":2498444,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"佢地唔小心講真話姐<br />\n班本土車迷重嬲緊佢去阿"},{"pid":"290a205d352cf8bd8ed0814cdd6333305d02414b","tid":2498444,"uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:39:43.000Z","msg":"口罩都唔識戴<br />\n戴番頭罩算啦"},{"pid":"c9aef077e7a8bda3d0bb1fa0ced5d9de87930441","tid":2498444,"uid":170521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"私了佢吖嘛!"},{"pid":"1e762066a823c14079f6ffcbcf9282ce214105e8","tid":2498444,"uid":581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/theeuropeanlad/status/1384560185272934406?s=21\" data-sr